      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "AC/DC FOREVER - High Voltage"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>More than just a tribute show, <b>High Voltage</b> presents a performance that perfectly captures the authenticity and energy of the legendary Australian band AC/DC.</p>\n\n<p>With over 17 years of experience and recognized by critics and audiences alike as the band offering the most realistic AC/DC show, <b>High Voltage</b> presents its show 'AC/DC Forever' in the largest venues in Quebec and Canada. They have also been chosen to perform with the Quebec City and Trois-Rivières symphony orchestras, a first in North America.</p>\n\n<p>Walls of amplifiers, multiple cannons, the iconic bell, not to mention the unmissable Rosie. It's all there!<br>\nAn evening with High Voltage is an evening with AC/DC, NOTHING LESS!</p>\n\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\ntw-seats-selectes-plv{display: none !important;}\n</style>\n"
      }
    ],
