    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "VMG Entertainment présente: Pooh - La Nostra Storia "
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>For six decades, POOH have been the soundtrack to generations of Italian music lovers around the world. Their songs are not just melodies — they are memories, emotions, and milestones in the lives of millions. In 2026, this legendary band celebrates an extraordinary 60 years of music with their anniversary tour 'POOH • La Nostra Storia', and Montréal will have the honor of hosting this historic celebration at the iconic Rialto Théâtre. This is more than a concert. It is a journey through time.</p>\n\n<p>From their beginnings in 1966 to becoming one of the most beloved and successful bands in Italian music history, POOH have created an unparalleled catalogue of timeless hits that continue to resonate across generations. Songs that filled homes, weddings, road trips, and family gatherings will come alive on stage in an unforgettable evening of nostalgia, emotion, and musical excellence.</p>\n\n<p>The majestic setting of the Rialto Théâtre provides the perfect backdrop for a night that promises to be both intimate and grand — a celebration of music, culture, and heritage that connects Montréal's vibrant Italian community to a piece of living history from Italy.</p>\n\n<p>Fans will be taken on a musical voyage through the band's most iconic songs, reliving the moments that made POOH a symbol of Italian artistry and passion. Whether you grew up listening to their records or discovered their music more recently, this performance will be a powerful reminder of why POOH's legacy has endured for 60 remarkable years.</p>\n\n<p>Prepare to sing, reminisce, and celebrate.</p>\n\n<p>POOH • La Nostra Storia — where memories meet music, and history comes alive in Montréal.</p>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;\n}\n</style>"
      }
    ],
